⭐️CONTEST!⭐️
Name our take home Margarita bag and win a free one for your next home fiesta! 1. Follow our profile @vatoscantinahv 2. Drop your entry in the comments below. Best name wins a free margarita bag with their next order so get creative! For more info read below (Swipe left for some home fiestas with our Margs!) .
.
🍹🍹🍹
Packing the punch of 3X Vatos Classic Margaritas ready for your home fiestas (210ml of alcohol, 675 ml total). Pre-mixed, includes lime wedges, vacuum packed and ready to go- just add ice! A great deal for only $24 (original price at outlet $45++) Only available for orders on Oddle and pickups.
.
💛💛💛
Thank you everyone for your posts and shares of your orders! Spread the word and we appreciate the support.
